This paper proposes a weakly supervised learning framework for clustering, which involves multiple instance learning and neural networks. The paper also discusses the potential use of the proposed method for zero-shot learning. Based on these topics, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
